    "excerpt": "It was early 2020, and it was a kind-of pre-pandemic world, where humans could roam around freely without worrying about the personal protective \"Armour\" named - mask. It was our third month into inc...",
    "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It was early 2020, and it was a kind-of pre-pandemic world, where humans could roam around freely without worrying about the personal protective \"Armour\" named - mask. It was our third month into inception, we met a nice guy, who manages a once-popular jewellers in our hometown. They were not doing that well online, they were being overshadowed by the new players, and they were having trouble competing with the new-gen bloods with the limited arsenal they had. We proposed that we will handle their website and SEO, and that changed their internet game forever. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fast forward to 2021 April, we are in another lockdown, and we had to submit the monthly reports, and we were flabbergasted. The growth they were able to achieve in a span of a year is one tremendous achievement. We are happy that our client is now savoring the fruit which we grew, the incredible growth of their online presence. Once neglected by the locals, is now home to one of the highest number of web visits for a jeweller's site in 2021. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This post will act as part anecdote, and part case study for this specific website. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Foreword</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The business is a heritage-chain of gold jewellers, having tremendously low online presence. Stakque Infotech pitched our idea of improving their website and done strategic changes in SEO for them. The end result was a promising and yet astounding growth for such a localized business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Strategy </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Heading - Faiz and Musi</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Conclusion</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This business is a prime example of how a committed effort with good strategy can actually do wonders in SEO. The client's requirements were aptly fullfilled by our team, without any delays </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->",
