    "title": "That's a Wrap! Adieu 2021",
    "slug": "that-s-a-wrap-adieu-2021",
    "excerpt": "2022 is around the corner. It is the perfect time for us to review what we were able to achieve in the 2021. This year was pretty happening one for us at Stakque Infotech. From having multiple office...",
    "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2022 is around the corner. It is the perfect time for us to review what we were able to achieve in the 2021. This year was pretty happening one for us at Stakque Infotech. From having multiple office, to improving the numbers it was totally a happening year for all of us at Stakque. <br><br>Multiple countries. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stakque Infotech has worked with clients from several countries in 2021. We had clients from India, China, Hong Kong, Qatar, United Arab Emirates, United States and Australia. Our clients have highly praised our digital marketing performance that we have generated for them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Social Media Results</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One of the core indicators of success in social media paid advertising landscape is total impressions, and whoa. The total ad impressions that we have generated in 2021 is 1,83,45,804 which is simply breathtaking. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>SEO Results</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stakque's SEO team has churned our some pretty awesome results for clients in general, bagging almost 350+ first page rankings for clients. Sigh! :D </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wrap Up</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Plans for 2021. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This will repeat every year until eternity. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->",
